settings.description: Mario Finds his castle and must go through it in order to win, the big bad bowser is waiting for him, but is it really the end? Bowser's Airship 1 is next.
Boom Boom gets his airship redesigned, now with a ton of fire! Make sure not to die! He is waiting for a challenge.
Not a Rip-off of an existing series called "The 8 Worlds" I swear. This is 1B, the underground pipe area part thing new area idea, what to name it tho?
Not a Rip-off of an existing series called "The 8 Worlds" I swear. Part 1A, this is the grassy land area. whatever you call it.

How to make your level goal look good:
Height should be 26, otherwise ending background will be one tile higher. Goal Roulette should be 8 tiles from right edge of the level and 5 tiles up from ground

No powerups? Come here to obtain "all" of them!
Shoe is not here. I will make a part 2. Soon.

Even if this editor seems kinda robust, it's kinda fun trying to build levels under the GBA's limitation. Level's mostly focused on the Triangular Block's mechanics.
Mario finds the actual bowser and Mario must defeat him! Don't die, this is bowsers final straw. This is the final level in this unnamed series.
